BIG BOSS BUSHMEN FULL WATCH – VERSION 1

A personal intrusion detection and alert system that watches all inbound
traffic to your device. It never touches external systems. Only your IP.

INSTALL:
1. Install Python 3
2. pip install scapy
3. On Windows: install Npcap
4. Run: python main.py

BACKGROUND MODE:
python run_service.py

